    public abstract static class TreeFitnessAbstract.TreeFitnessGUISettingsAbstract<F extends TreeFitnessAbstract>
extends com.fluxicon.slickerbox.components.RoundedPanel
    An abstract instance of a GUI interface to set up a TreeFitness metric. A metric that requires additional user input, should declare a (local) public class extending this abstract class and overwrite the static function getGUISettingsPanel(ETMParam param) from this class and return their declared GUI instance.
